Heat olive oil in a skillet over medium heat. 2. Add diced onion, bell pepper, and jalapeno. Cook until softened. 3. In a separate skillet, place one tortilla. 4. Sprinkle with shredded cheddar cheese. 5. Layer with shredded chicken and cooked vegetables. 6. Top with another tortilla. 7. Cook until cheese is melted and tortilla is golden brown. 8. Repeat for the remaining tortillas. 9.
